content.rendered:
Directed by Navneet Behal.

Written by Maitrey Bajpai. Maitrey Bajpai. Maitrey Bajpai. Ramiz Ilham Khan.

Cast Pravessh Rana(Prakash (as Parvesh Rana)). Kay Kay Menon(Govind). Kirti Kulhari(Meena). Tom Alter(Irish). Shubham(Baansath (62) (as Shubham Is)). Muaz Hasan(Kannu). Danish Khan(Mannu) . Raghav Chadha(German). Uday Chandra(Major Thapar). Vishwanath Chatterjee(Gorakhnath). Dheerendra Dwivedi(Kedarnath). Harshit Gupta(Munna (as Harshid Gupta)). Asifa Jamaa(Babita Negi). Jasbeer(Iqbal). Mushtaq Kak(Liaqat Sanda). Ehsan Khan(Saxena). Nadeem(Side (voice)). Nadeem(Mehboob). Govind Pandey(Ramavtar). Pushpendra Saxena(Ibrahim Chacha). Mukesh Sharma(Bhediya). Rajesh Sharma(Bakery Man). Vishnu Tripath(Dr. Atmanand). Saurabh Yadav(Guy 1 who escapes from jail)

Language Hindi.

Producers Rasika Banerjee. Kabir Lovee. Neytiri S.. Ajeet Singh.

Production Pehle Aap Motion Pictures.
